OL,3,CConvicted rapist attacked woman after
OL,4,Cleaving open prison
OL,6,FA judge has called for an
OL,7,Finvestigation after a convicted rapist
OL,8,Fattacked a woman having absconded from
OL,9,Fprison day release for a second time.
OL,11,FNeil Trennan, 61, was handed his third
OL,12,Flife sentence for assaulting a student
OL,13,Fwhile on unsupervised day release from
OL,14,FHMP North Sea Camp in Lincolnshire
OL,15,Flast year.
OL,17,FTrennan was first jailed for life in
OL,18,F1991 for breaking into a woman's home
OL,19,Fin Sheffield, hitting her in the head
OL,20,Fwith a dumbbell and raping her while
OL,21,Fshe was unconscious.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
