OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772062285
OL,3,CConvicted rapist attacked woman after
OL,4,Cleaving open prison
OL,6,FHe was handed a second life sentence
OL,7,Fin 2002 after escaping from a
OL,8,F"distracted" prison officer while on
OL,9,Fday release in Norwich, going into a
OL,10,Fwomen's toilet and hitting a woman
OL,11,Fwith a brick.
OL,13,FSheffield Crown Court heard Trennan
OL,14,Fhad previously confessed to parole
OL,15,Fboards throughout his time in jail
OL,16,Fthat he was aroused by violence and
OL,17,F"enjoyed 'violent, non-consensual sex".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]yD@AOUyD@fO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
