CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772062285
OL,3,CConvicted rapist attacked woman after
OL,4,Cleaving open prison
OL,6,FIn July last year he was on day
OL,7,Frelease from prison in Lincolnshire
OL,8,Fwhen he travelled to Sheffield,
OL,9,Ffollowed a student into her house and
OL,10,Fstarted to attack her while armed with
OL,11,Fa knife.
OL,13,FThe court heard the woman managed to
OL,14,Fknock the knife from his hand and
OL,15,Flocked herself in the bathroom.
OL,17,FA judge said if the student had not
OL,18,Fmanaged to fight him off, Trennan
OL,19,Fwould have subjected her to a violent
OL,20,Frape.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
