OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772062285
OL,3,CConvicted rapist attacked woman after
OL,4,Cleaving open prison
OL,6,FOn Wednesday Judge Jeremy Richardson
OL,7,FKC, the Recorder of Sheffield, gave
OL,8,FTrennan a third life sentence, with a
OL,9,Fminimum term of 10 years, but said it
OL,10,Fwould likely never be safe for him to
OL,11,Fbe released from prison.
OL,13,FJudge Richardson said it was "very
OL,14,Funwise" for Trennan to have been
OL,15,Fallowed any form of unsupervised
OL,16,Frelease "given what was known about
OL,17,F(him)".
OL,26,@uD@^OUvD@GO]xD@IOUyD@FO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772062285
OL,3,CConvicted rapist attacked woman after
OL,4,Cleaving open prison
OL,6,FThe judge said he had "been given no
OL,7,Fadequate explanation for the decision"
OL,8,Fbut would send his sentencing remarks
OL,9,Fto the Lord Chancellor, who "may
OL,10,Fdemand one".
OL,12,FJudge Richardson said: "This is an
OL,13,Fappalling case of history repeating
OL,14,Fitself and of insufficient heed being
OL,15,Ftaken of that history when you were
OL,16,Fplaced in open prison conditions.
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@fO]qD@]OUrD@KO]tD@XOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
