FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1772062285
OL,3,CConvicted rapist attacked woman after
OL,4,Cleaving open prison
OL,6,F"That must never happen again. As I
OL,7,Fhave stated you pose immense and
OL,8,Fenduring dangers to women of acute
OL,9,Fviolence and associated sexual
OL,10,Fdepravity.
OL,12,F"No woman is safe whilst ever you
OL,13,Fremain at large."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@QO]
